            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm plant-theme p-3 h-100">
                    <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-2"><i class="bi bi-seedling me-2"></i>Our Mission</h4>
                    <p class="small mb-0">Empowering plant lovers and nursery owners to nurture, manage, and grow their green spaces with ease and joy.</p>
